    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## AI as a Debate Partner\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to engage in a debate about a topic of your choice.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Start with a **broad, open-ended debate prompt** (e.g., \"Should schools ban homework?\" or \"Is AI better at making decisions than humans?\").\r\n2. Read **AI Chat’s response**, then **counter** its argument by providing an opposing viewpoint.\r\n3. **Revise your prompt** by making it more specific (e.g., \"Argue why schools should ban homework for middle school students.\").\r\n4. **Upload an image** related to your debate topic (e.g., a news article screenshot, a relevant chart, or a meme) and see how AI’s response changes.\r\n5. **Compare AI’s responses**—how did the AI adjust its reasoning as your inputs became more refined?\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**",
